    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The building trades council held a\nmeeting last night. but nothing of\nconsequence was done with regard to\nthe millworkers' strike and the Inland\nMill & Manufacturing company. Har-\ncleroad- Westphal Mill company. King\nSash & Door company and the Post\nFalls Sash & Door company. which\nwere placed on the unfair list by the\ntrades council. The stock for the new\nmill which the strikers propose to\nbuild Is selling rapidly. An outline\nOF where the engines and saws are\nto set has been made for the archi-\ntect who was given the work of max\ning the plans today."
    }
